##A life saving moment for small and micro businesses

Function introduction, the interface news is China has the influence original financial and economic new media, only serves the independent thinking crowd

"Some say that a grain of sand from the age is a mountain on an individual's head. I feel like I've been carrying Mount Everest for a month now,"says the author of the amateur-writing Baman Rice noodles, as he looks back at the company's recent life-and-death moments.

After graduating from university in 2014, Zhang Tianyi, with his "post-90s master degree from Peking University" Halo, founded Baman Rice noodles, a restaurant brand that sells offline. Flash 5 years later, BA man rice noodles in the country has 60 offline directly operated stores, of which Beijing has 40, basically covering the major shopping centers in Beijing.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Rice noodles

Confident Zhang Tianyi in late 2019 press the development fast-forward button, made the decision to open more than a dozen new stores. "starting today, one new store a day will open until the year 30, " he wrote on his facebook page

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Zhang Tianyi friend circle

Unexpectedly, a sudden outbreak of "Black Swan" , Baman instant rice noodles into the cold winter, the line of 60 stores income is basically 0, can be said to be no harvest, a month but to spend nearly 20 million costs. Cash flow is the lifeline of small and micro enterprises, with the cash flow situation at the time, Baman Rice noodles last less than two months.

But the turnaround soon appeared, Zhang Tianyi Accident Discovery, tmall brand store channel background data that did not pay attention to before, semi-finished rice noodle sales growth significantly. The East side is not bright, the west side is bright, he resolutely concentrated manpower line. From February 11 to February 28, BA man rice noodles in tmall a total of about 80,000 parcels, directly sold out of stock. The goods were sent out, but according to the rules of Alibaba's e-commerce platform, it requires consumers to click "confirm receipt" after receiving the goods, so that the seller can get the sales refund. The time difference is still very long, the cash flow is still hanging over the head of the Damocles.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Zhang Tianyi himself

Life and death, Zhang Tianyi always pay close attention to the various platforms of business support measures. On February 10, Ali and his Ant Financial released alibaba's letter to merchants, which aims to support businesses and fight the epidemic together with small and medium-sized enterprises, it offers low interest and interest free loans to businesses, subsidizes couriers to make logistics move faster, provides flexible jobs that allow employees to work and earn money, opens up more digital capabilities for businesses, and helps companies work and manage remotely.

On February 19th Ali laid out more than 20 rules on how to help businesses. Among them, clean out treasure provides free"collect money in advance"service for the businessman, the businessman wants to send goods only hind can apply to be paid by net merchant bank advance money, do"0 Account Period". This solves the immediate problem of Baman Rice noodles. Through TMALL 0 Account Back to the initiative, BA man rice noodles to withdraw a total of 6.6 million yuan in cash, successfully through the door of death.

"I have also compared other banks' loan products, but due to the long credit cycle and the fact that our catering companies don't have too much collateral, the credit line is not big, " Zhang told interface news, "thanks to TMALL's zero payment, it has really supported our start-up business and is one of the strongest and most timely financial support policies we have enjoyed during the most difficult period of the epidemic. "

As an open platform for e commerce, Ali's policy of helping businesses is not only to relieve the pressure of cash flow, but also to teach people how to fish. 'tmall is concerned about the difficulties of a restaurant company like us, and has contacted us to explore whether we can use tmall and our stores to complete more e-commerce transformation, ' Zhang said. "after discovering the demand of E-commerce, ba-man rice noodles went on to restock super channels such as Hema as quickly as possible. Our semi-finished instant rice noodles also appeared on the shelves and sold out. "

Ideas Open, Zhang Tianyi said will use the Baman Rice noodles online operation capacity to help more catering enterprises. It is understood that BA man rice line to start to help catering enterprises on behalf of the operation of e-commerce business, now has a catering customer partner and its entry into the signing process.

In fact, during the epidemic, "zero account period" saved not only a small and micro-enterprises, focus on essential oil make-up fu essential oil is also "zero account period" beneficiaries.

It is understood that after the Spring Festival, Fu essential oil in rent, wages, publicity and promotion on the cumulative expenditure of more than 20 million yuan, but the sale of natural recovery is very slow, has been a net overdraft state.

"Due to the stoppage of express delivery and the non-resumption of work at the Logistics Park, we receive less than one-tenth of the money back every day from our sales, and the cash flow of the enterprise is under great pressure, " Yang Yin, head of the e-commerce Company for Afu essential oil, told reporters, the company used TMALL's zero billing support policy to get a $5 million quick refund, which gave the overdrawn aphrodisiac oil a week or so of relief, significantly eased the company's cash pressure.

Also under pressure was the Guqin Player, Wang Ning. In order to promote his guqin skills, four years ago he gave up his position as a grass-roots official at Huawei and his annual salary of 800,000 yuan. Instead, he turned himself into a master of Guqin and ran a Guqin Club called the Luhe Qin Club in Beijing, at present, he has some influence in the local music circle of Beijing. Because the Guqin requires a high level of time and craftsmanship, and in the face of rare raw materials, as well as the financial losses caused by the repeated relocation of workshops (due to policy reasons such as the transformation of shanty towns) , still in the start-up and continuous investment period, Wang Ning had to use the online business loans to do some capital turnover.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Piano Club

After the arrival of the epidemic, with a semi-public nature of the Piano Club offline revenue source cut off, online business volume increased, but online sales to not make money or even lose money scattered string majority. Many players had plenty of time to play at home during the outbreak, and the strings were expendable, so orders for a single string were probably two to three times higher than usual. Plus there was a warehouse in the village, so the outbreak couldn't be used and Wang Ning had to restock it. For a time, Wang Ning's financial pressure increased sharply, purely rely on their own funds are inevitably overstretched.

"The zero account period offered by Taobao.com, which can quickly recover some of the money already shipped, can really solve the pressing problem of more rapid and more stock to improve service capacity, " said Wang Ning, a communications engineer by training, the operation of the Taobao Merchant Bank is very simple. A few clicks on the mobile phone will take a few seconds to arrive in the account. He knows very well that this can not be done without the hard work of the Ali people and the support of powerful technology, and for Ali people "warm feelings shop owners, Technology Service Micro" the spirit of praise.

At present, the outbreak of the new pneumonia epidemic is still continuing, delayed resumption of work, business blocked, micro, small and medium-sized enterprises were hit.

Money is food for battle. Previously, a survey conducted by 995 small and medium-sized enterprises jointly conducted by Tsinghua University and Peking University showed that if the epidemic continues, 85% of enterprises'cash flow can be maintained for up to three months. How to ensure cash flow has become the key to the survival of enterprises. At the same time, 70 per cent said they were confident that business would pick up as long as money was flowing.

On March 2, E-commerce Bank and Taobao jointly launched an initiative to urge the whole society to shorten the accounting period of small and medium-sized enterprises, not to intercept and default, and to protect their capital chain; E-commerce Bank will advance 50-100 billion yuan, and together with Taobao, first practice the "zero accounting period. ".

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
ALIBABA initiative

Merchants can apply for payment by the bank after shipment, to facilitate the expansion of reproduction, capital costs and risks by Taobao platform and the bank to bear. Taobao launched the first domestic e-commerce platform free "0 Account Period" service, as as soon as delivery can collect money, to ease the cash flow pressure of small and medium-sized enterprises to provide a great support. This is the lowest threshold to ease the pressure of cash flow measures.

At the same time, alipay also called everyone after receiving satisfaction, the first time to confirm the receipt of goods, merchants received money one minute earlier. Recently, Taobao on the new 7 million consumers to confirm receipt of goods, to help businesses early to collect funds.

According to the initiative, all of the 6.5 million eligible Taobao merchants can apply for early payment after delivery. Before consumers confirm receipt of the goods, the online merchant bank will advance payment for the consumers; consumers can continue to enjoy the safe experience of the alipay guaranteed transaction, protection of rights and interests will not be affected. The service will be available for free until March 31.

It is worth mentioning that consumers are also quietly helping businesses to shorten the payback time. "I order the goods at once" "stick to it" has become the most frequent conversation between consumers and business before.

Li Haitao, a finance professor and Associate Dean at the Cheung Kong Graduate School of Business, said small and medium sized enterprises were responsible for a large number of jobs in China and that liquidity and cash flow were crucial to their survival after the epidemic. One day shorter, one step faster. The appeal of E-commerce Bank and Taobao is very necessary. The platform sacrifices its own short-term interests to carry out precision drip irrigation, which brings stability and development of millions of micro-and medium-sized enterprises.
